Label: UVRAG complex
Comment: The PIK3C3-containing Beclin-1 complex consists of PIK3C3 (Vps34), BECN1 (Beclin-1, Atg6), PIK3R4 (p150, Vps15) and ATG14 (Barkor) (Matsunaga et al. 2009, Zhong et al. 2009). Binding of KIAA0226 to this complex negatively regulates the maturation process (Matsunaga et al. 2009).
